<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="another-pron">another <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'nʌðə(r)/    美 /ə'nʌðər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>又一个；再一个；另一个：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don’t like this hat. Show me another.
我不喜欢这顶帽子，再给我拿一顶。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="one-after-another">one after another</h3>
<p>1.<strong>陆续地；一个接一个地</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="one-another">one another</h3>
<p>1.<strong>互相</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="one-thing-another">one thing ... another ...</h3>
<p>1.<strong>一回事…另一回事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Saying is one thing and doing another.
说是一回事，做又是另一回事。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Recycling is one way to protect the environment;reusing is <strong><em>_</em></strong>_.  （2013 重庆改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. another  </p></div>